                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2">
                        API 키는 로컬에 저장되며 외부로 전송되지 않습니다.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-6">
                    <div class="bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <h4 class="text-blue-300 font-medium mb-2 flex items-center">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle mr-2"></i>API 키 발급 방법
                        </h4>
                        <ol class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1">
                            <li>1. <a href="https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Google AI Studio</a>에 접속</li>
                            <li>2. "Create API key" 클릭</li>
                            <li>3. 프로젝트 선택 후 API 키 생성</li>
                            <li>4. 생성된 키를 복사하여 위에 붙여넣기</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex space-x-3">
                    <button id="saveGeminiApiKey" 
                            class="flex-1 bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-save"></i>
                        <span>저장</span>
                    </button>
                    <button id="testGeminiApiKey" 
                            class="flex-1 bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <span>테스트</span>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div id="geminiApiStatus" class="mt-4 hidden">
                    <!-- API 상태 메시지 영역 -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

